<L>__{exterior empire state building observation deck dusk into}
<B>__{night}
<A>__{jonah is looking through the viewfinder. he turns around, forlorn. he takes off his backpack and is about to sit down next to it when sam bolts into the observation deck. jonah leaps into his arms.}
<C>__{sam}
<D>__{you're my family. you're all i've got. what if something happened to you?}
<A>__{sam's eyes well up. jonah starts to cry.}
<C>__{sam}
<D>__{what if i couldn't get to you?}
<C>__{jonah}
<D>__{i was scared of what you were gonna do.}
<C>__{sam}
<D>__{when i found you?}
<C>__{jonah}
<D>__{if i didn't go.}
<C>__{sam}
<D>__{listen, have i ever done anything really stupid?}
<C>__{jonah}
<D>__{no.}
<C>__{sam}
<D>__{i mean, so far, have i screwed it up for you?}
<C>__{jonah}
<D>__{no.}
<A>__{the two of them hold each other tight. after a beat:}
<C>__{sam}
<D>__{i can't believe you flew first class.}
<C>__{jonah}
<D>__{it was all they had.}
